author: Taegan Goddard
title: Biden Lost the Invisible Primary
text:
Biden Lost the Invisible Primary October 21, 2015 By Taegan Goddard 0 Comments 
Perry Bacon : “Vice President Joe Biden officially decided not to run for president. But in many ways, it wasn’t his choice: the power brokers in the Democratic Party unified around former Secretary of State Hillary Clinton, not the sitting vice president, leaving Biden the options of either not running or facing a campaign with long odds of victory.” Related Posts Never miss a Political Wire post Your email address: * Please enter all required fields Correct invalid entries
